{"tid":2195520,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"12港人好快會認罪再自願坐監","createTime":"2020-09-09T08:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T11:42:42.000Z","uid":231886,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"beb14169ed7f72a3bd0c52a7dd03b1d6913c84c3","tid":2195520,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T08:37:44.000Z","msg":"因為...<br />\n<br />\n【突發！12港人最新消息】<br />\n<br />\n由港人家屬委託辯護的盧思位律師表示，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">鹽田看守所警官指，其當事人已另外「委托」了兩名律師跟進</span></span>，因此不會安排會面。<br />\n<br />\n該兩名律師相信是由中共直接安排的官方律師。<br />\n<br />\n[Breaking: latest update for the 12]<br />\n<br />\nThe officers of the Detention Centre told Mr Lu Siwei, a lawyer instructed by family member, that his client has already &ldquo;instructed&rdquo; two other lawyers to follow the case, therefore they will NOT arrange a visit for Mr Lu. <br />\n<br />\nThe above-mentioned lawyers are believed to be directly appointed by the authorities.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />共產黨幫你安排律師，順手幫埋你認罪，劇本好快就會實行"},{"pid":"34a23fe3dd58b97006f738666d620ad851271940","tid":2195520,"uid":44318,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T08:38:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deffcedae141e6becd2332b4258710af0e09cf11","tid":2195520,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T08:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f9d4d81c3fa0281fb703653c246628e60d9715","tid":2195520,"uid":108213,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T08:40:25.000Z","msg":"預左被委托 <br />\n一貫做法"},{"pid":"19c001433643f0edb49e0119526949d577fa45f3","tid":2195520,"uid":17705,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T08:41:40.000Z","msg":"掛黃圈名賺到盤滿砵滿嗰啲去咗邊<br />\n<br />\n唔好令我傷心"},{"pid":"443cc8d902ee2326e230e0c64161ca8952bcd8f1","ti